title: Is ALRED MUTUA taking shots at WILLIAM RUTO over looting of public money, Truth...
content: – A video of Machakos Governor Alfred Mutua calling out corrupt senior Government leaders has left people guessing that he is taking shots at Deputy President William Ruto.    William Ruto has been buying property from right, left and centre and his source of wealth is shrouded in mystery.    His salary doesn’t match his investments.    If you listen to this video of Mutua carefully, then you will understand who he is referring to.    Watch it.    The Kenyan DAILY POST    Continue Reading
